com.diffplug.common.swt

Class TypedDataField<T,W extends Widget>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.diffplug.common.swt.TypedDataField<T,W>

  • public class TypedDataField<T,W extends Widget>
extends Object
    Typed utility for getting and setting data using SWT's Widget getData() / setData() API. ``` TypedDataField field = TypedDataField.create("model"); Model model = field.get(widget); field.set(widget, model); ```
